These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, ice-hockey, weightlifting, rugby
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, july, april, november
House: colonial, cottage, craftsman, townhouse
The people have 4 different jobs:  social-worker, musician, dressmaker, police-officer
 1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3
 2. the craftsman house is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the townhouse house is the person who's birthday is in july##1
 5. the social-worker is somewhere to the left of the dressmaker##5
 6. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the left of the musician##5
 7. the cottage house is on the far left##1
 8. the dressmaker is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##5
 9. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
10. the townhouse house is somewhere between the social-worker and the person who's sport is surfing##7
11. the townhouse house is on the right of the craftsman house##1
12. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere to the right of the police-officer##5
13. the police-officer is the townhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Sport   | rugby    | ice-hockey | weightlifting    | surfing   |
| Birthday   | may | april | july | november |
| House           | cottage       | craftsman   | townhouse  | colonial     |
| Job     | social-worker      | dressmaker   | police-officer    | musician    |

