.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-2::.
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, snooker, backgammon, billiard
4 different pets are kept: bird, rabbit, hedgehog, pony
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, drawing, rock-climbing, sudoku
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, april, july, august
 1. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##5
 2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##5
 3. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the right of the person playing billiard##5
 4. the person who's birthday is in july is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 5. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3
 6. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the right of the person playing backgammon##5
 7. the person playing billiard is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who's hobby is video-games##7
 8. the person playing mah-jongg is in an odd position##4
 9. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##5
10. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##5
11. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |       3       |     4      |
| Game          | mah-jongg   | backgammon       | billiard    | snooker      |
| Pet   | bird | pony | rabbit         | hedgehog   |
| Hobby   | sudoku   | video-games  | drawing       | rock-climbing |
| Birthday         | february      | july  | august | april |

