 3. the person eating lettuce is somewhere to the left of the fan jazz##5
 4. the fan salsa is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
 5. the person eating lettuce is somewhere to the left of the fan salsa##5
 6. the person who likes lilac is on the left or right of the fan funk##3
 7. the person eating lettuce is somewhere between the person who likes grey and the person who likes lilac##7
 8. the person eating peach is not the person who likes grey##6
 9. the person who likes red is on the left or right of the person who likes lilac##3
10. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the fan salsa##1
11. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
12. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |       4       |
| Food         | garlic      | lettuce   | peach   | spinach       |
| Cigar   | siglo | dunhill    | old-henry | bongani       |
| Music-Genre   | blues  | funk | salsa   | jazz     |
| Color         | grey   | chestnut    | lilac   | red |

