The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, lily, daisy, rose
 1. the person who growsrose is somewhere to the left of the person who growsorchid##5
 2. the person traveling to san-francisco is the prince-smoker##1
 3. the person who growslily is the person who likes pink##1
 4. the person who likes red is between the havana-smoker and the oliveros-smoker##2
 5. the person traveling to berlin is somewhere to the right of the oliveros-smoker##5
 6. the person who likes lilac is somewhere between the person traveling to san-francisco and the aristoff-smoker##7
 7. the havana-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to hannover##5
 8. the person who likes lilac is the person who growsorchid##1
 9. the person traveling to hannover is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to berlin##5
10. the person who likes blood-red is on the far right##1
11. the person who growsdaisy is in an even position##4
12. the person traveling to berlin is somewhere to the right of the oliveros-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
